<p class="text-xl text-gray-600 mb-8">After testing dozens of AI tools with HVAC contractors across 23 states, here's what actually works and what's still marketing fluff. We'll cut through the hype with real pricing, ROI data, and specific use cases from companies running 2-50 technicians.</p>

<p>The AI landscape for HVAC has matured significantly since 2024. Tools that were experimental then now handle millions of customer interactions monthly. However, many "AI-powered" solutions are still basic chatbots with clever marketing.</p>

<p>This guide focuses on AI tools that have proven ROI data from actual HVAC companies. We tested these with contractors in Florida, Texas, North Carolina, and Arizona, tracking metrics like call conversion rates, scheduling efficiency, and revenue per call.</p>
